        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>作为第一篇文章，此文用作本博客markdown (.md)格式写作参考</p><a id="more"></a><!-- 关于抬头格式 --><!-- comments: false (如果不需要评论则加上) --><!-- reward: false (如果需要捐助则删掉) --><!-- mathjax: true (实际上用的是Latex格式) --><!-- 以下为正文 --><h1 id="Head-部分"><a href="#Head-部分" class="headerlink" title="Head 部分"></a>Head 部分</h1><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 博文框架</span><br><span class="line">date: 2019-06-20 00:00:00</span><br><span class="line">categories: </span><br><span class="line">  - 学习</span><br><span class="line">  - hexo</span><br><span class="line">  - markdown</span><br><span class="line">tags: [blog,模板]</span><br><span class="line">reward: false</span><br><span class="line">mathjax: true</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">作为第一篇文章，此文用作本博客markdown (.md)格式写作参考</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- more --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- 关于抬头格式 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- comments: false (如果不需要评论则加上) --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- reward: false (如果需要捐助则删掉) --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- mathjax: true (实际上用的是Latex格式) --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- 以下为正文 --&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="如何新建一篇-post"><a href="#如何新建一篇-post" class="headerlink" title="如何新建一篇 post"></a>如何新建一篇 post</h1><p>命令：<br><figure class="highlight taggerscript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">C:<span class="symbol">\U</span>sers<span class="symbol">\.</span>..<span class="symbol">\b</span>log&gt; hexo n post &lt;新的博客名称&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>新的博客自动采用上文中的模板，代码如下（在终端没有hexo工具包的情况下可以先复制这里的模板使用，等之后有机会再推送）：<br><figure class="highlight twig"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="xml">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">title: </span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123; title &#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">date: </span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123; <span class="name">date</span> &#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">categories: </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">  - 一级分类</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">  - 二级分类 （非必须）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">  - 三级分类 （非必须）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">tags: [blog,模板]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">reward: false</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">mathjax: true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">这里是摘要</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">Abstract</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- more --&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- 关于抬头格式 --&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- comments: false (如果不需要评论则加上) --&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- reward: false (如果需要捐助则删掉) --&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- mathjax: true (实际上用的是Latex格式) --&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- 以下为正文 --&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- 结尾参考文献及中文版权声明 --&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"># 参考文献</span></span><br><span clas